# 🐞 Checkbox text "general.spheres.choice.advertising" is not fully visible in Vacancies section

**Bug ID:** BUG-001  
**Priority:** Medium  
**Severity:** Normal  

---

## Description
In the Vacancies section, one checkbox label is not fully visible while scrolling the filter panel.

---

## Preconditions
- User is on the website  
- Vacancies page is open  
- Filter panel is visible  

---

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Open the website: https://www.example.com/  
2. Click on the "Vacancies" button  
3. Scroll down the filter panel  

---

## Actual Result
The label **"general.spheres.choice.advertising"** is truncated and displayed as  
**"general.spheres.choice.adv"**  

---

## Expected Result
All checkbox labels should be fully visible and displayed consistently. 
